summary: This is Persuasion's Armor. Persuasion's Armor make speechcraft 100% better. It can be found The Warrens (Eltry's Room).  Don't take this armor seriously it is a little bit overpowered but it's fun.
descriptionHtml: [size=4]Persuasion's Armor is a light ebony armor which can be found in Eltry's Room, The Warrens. This armor is a little bit of a joke. It is my first mod so give me a break if anyone one installs this mod, Thank You! If you want me to give this Armor a backstory i will. I hope you enjoy this mod thank you.[/size]
